1. *Loptu* je on bacio u vazduh. (He threw the ball in the air.)
2. On je prihvatio *loptu*. (He accepted the ball.)
3. Ona je izgubila *loptu*. (She lost the ball.)
4. Ona je lako uhvatila *loptu*. (She easily caught the ball.)
5. Ona je vratila *loptu*. (She returned the ball.)
6. On je pokazao *loptu*. (He showed the ball.)
7. Oni su lako odbacili *loptu*. (They easily bounced the ball.)
